[para]
[:en] For a function or function template [$F] defined in this subclause,
let [$C] be its associated class template.
[:zh_CN] 对于本子条款中定义的函数或函数模板 [$F]，令 [$C] 为其关联类模板。

[:en] For the evaluation of a call to [$F], let [$S] be the specialization of [$C]
in terms of which the call is specified.
[:zh_CN] 对于一次对 [$F] 调用的求值，令 [$S] 为依据此调用所指定的 [$C] 的特例。

[list]
[item]
[:en] If
[:zh_CN] 如果
 [list]
 [item]
[:en@~] the template arguments of [$S] violate a condition specified
in a [=Mandates] element in the specification of [$C];
[:zh_CN@~] [$S] 的各模板实参违反了 [$C] 的规范中某项[=Mandates]元素中规定的条件；
 [item]
[:en@~] the call is specified to produce a reflection of a type,
but [$S] would have no member named [`type]; or
[:zh_CN@~] 此调用被指定为产生一个类型的反射，但 [$S] 没有名为 [`type] 的成员；但
 [item]
[:en@~] the call is specified to return [`[$S]::value], but that expression
would not be a valid converted constant expression of type [`R], where [`R] is
the return type of [$F];
[:zh_CN@~] 此调用被指定为返回 [`[$S]::value]，但该表达式不是有效的 [`R] 类型的
经转换常量表达式，其中 [`R] 为 [$F] 的返回类型；
 [list:end]
[:en@~] then an exception of type [`meta::exception] is thrown.
[:zh_CN@~] 则抛出 [`meta::exception] 类型的异常。

[begin:note]
[:en] For the first case, [$S] is not instantiated.
[:zh_CN] 第一种情况，不实例化 [$S]。
[end:note]

[item]
[:en] Otherwise, if the instantiation of [$S] would result in undefined behavior
due to dependence on an incomplete type ([#meta.rqmts]), then the call is not
a constant subexpression.
[:zh_CN] 否则，如果 [$S] 的实例化会因依赖于某个不完整类型而导致未定义行为（[#meta.rqmts]），
则此调用不是常量子表达式。

[item]
[:en] Otherwise, if the template arguments of [$S] do not meet the preconditions of [$C],
then it is unspecified whether the call is a constant subexpression.
[:zh_CN] 否则，如果 [$S] 的各模板实参不满足 [$C] 的前条件，则未指明此调用是否是常量子表达式。

[:en] If it is, the call produces the result that would be produced if [$C] had no preconditions.
[:zh_CN] 如果它是，则此调用产生当 [$C] 没有前条件时会产生的结果。
[list:end]

[para]
[:en] Each function or function template declared above has the following behavior
based on the signature and return type of that function or function template.
[:zh_CN] 以上声明的每个函数或函数模板，基于该函数或函数模板的签名和返回类型，具有下列行为。

[begin:note]
[:en] The associated class template need not be instantiated.
[:zh_CN] 不需要实例化关联的类模板。
[end:note]

