[codeblock:end]

[div:description]
[para:returns]
[:en] [`std::variant_size<[$T]>::value], where [$T] is the type represented by [`dealias(type)].
[:zh_CN] [`std::variant_size<[$T]>::value]，其中 [$T] 为 [`dealias(type)] 所表示的类型。
