[:en] A reflection representing the type denoted by [`std::variant_alternative<[$I], [$T]>::type],
where [$T] is the type represented by [`dealias(type)] and [$I] is a constant equal to [`index].
[:zh_CN] 表示 [`std::variant_alternative<[$I], [$T]>::type] 所代表的类型的反射，
其中 [$T] 为 [`dealias(type)] 所表示的类型，而 [$I] 为等于 [`index] 的常量。
