[%@lib type_order]
[codeblock:declaration]
consteval strong_ordering type_order(info t1, info t2);
[codeblock:end]

[div:description]
[para:returns]
[:en] [`std::type_order<[$T_1], [$T_2]>::value], where [$T_1] and [$T_2] are the types
represented by [`dealias(t1)] and [`dealias(t2)], respectively.
[:zh_CN] [`std::type_order<[$T_1], [$T_2]>::value]，其中 [$T] 和 [$T_2] 分别为
[`dealias(t1)] 和 [`dealias(t2)] 所表示的类型。
[div:end]
